title: Finest upscale living! 2 bed / 2 bath! HANA Apartments
posting_body: ['HANA Apartments - A place to call home!', 'Bed: 2 / Bath: 2', 'Sq.', 'Footage: 796 - 930 sq ft', 'Rent: $2032/Month', 'Terms: 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month, 16-Month, 17-Month, 18-Month', 'show contact info', 'Uncompromising quality is a hallmark of our homes as evidenced by features such as hardwood-style flooring and other modern finishes.', 'Thoughtfully crafted layouts cater to convenience and comfort with washer and dryer hookups, oversized windows and sustainable design.', 'The modern kitchens are equipped with hard-surface countertops and brand new appliances.', 'Our Apartment Homes Feature:', '● Brand New Appliances', '● Hard Surface Counters', '● Hardwood Style Flooring', '● Kitchen', '● Rentable Washer and Dryer', '● Washer and Dryer Hook-Ups', '● Water, Sewer, and Trash Included in Rent', '● Wi-Fi', '● City Views in Select Homes', '● Energy Efficient', '● Large Windows', '● Modern Finishes', '● Smart Layouts', '● Water View in Select Homes', '● Wood Inspired Flooring', 'Our Residents Enjoy:', '● Accepts Electronic Payments', '● Bike Storage', '● Controlled Access', '● Lounge', '● Online Leasing', '● Onsite Maintenance', '● Onsite Management', '● 3-Star Built Green', '● Barbecue Pits for Cooking Out on the Roof Deck', '● Controlled Access Bike Storage', '● Controlled Access Building', '● Controlled Access Rentable Parking', '● Convenient State of the Art Laundry Rooms', '● Resident Lounge and Full Kitchen with WiFi located off the Roof Deck', '● Roof Deck with City and Water Views', 'Contact Info:', 'show contact info', '101 6th Ave S', 'Seattle, WA 98104', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Pets:', 'HANA Apartments is a pet-friendly community.', 'We allow two (2) pets max per household.', '$35/pet rent and a $300 pet deposit.', 'Weight limit: 25 lbs.', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'C24076894D2E49B']
